      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Nations",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Heavenly Principles",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "When the Primordial One was wounded and lost some of their functions, they created the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4935,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/15/94376896/d233949972be14fcf0feb738a9b67efa_4817492893140404510.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Gnosis",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "and declared the Archon War, a war between the gods of Teyvat for the right to ascend to the divine throne and obtain a Gnosis. Only one deity from each region could become an Archon, while all others had to abdicate the throne or be defeated.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3796,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/26/237301566/a19531bd8e93b793b79bfe1499b5b5d7_7637529122280724157.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Мондштадт",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "After the rebellion in Mondstadt 2,600 years ago, an elemental spirit, Barbatos, became the first Anemo Archon.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3797,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/12/237301566/5968bc73f375ee1e3704302541c83c7f_5877733374426459671.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Ли Юэ",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "After the Archon War,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "became the first Geo Archon.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3798,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/237301566/fe011f0f93e3259d28b0272d0db961b7_1186066791860134492.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Инадзума",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "During the war,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4907,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Makoto",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "became the first Electro Archon of Inazuma. According to a legend, her twin sister Ei sacrificed her physical body so Makoto could ascend to the divine throne.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3799,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/237301566/f77d0c308b54728b6a1f3bc525e42955_1619892372187600936.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Сумеру",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "There was no Archon War in Sumeru.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "declined the divine throne that was offered by Celestia and ruled along with",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4912,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/03/237301566/513d51e0ebfd54f5da34a9f85dfaf61f_4293187669096717509.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Набу Маликата",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "and",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4910,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/03/237301566/59da6a8cbcffa112e5d2b63788d7051e_1480677671668697202.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Руккхадевата",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". After Al-Ahmar and Nabu Malikata's deaths, Greater Lord Rukkhadevata became the first Dendro Archon.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3979,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/237301566/decfebf39c4d3b6e22cf9f28c98288f6_1758697124608038722.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Фонтейн",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "There was no Archon War in Fontaine. After the Golden Empire,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4813,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/29/237301566/4f78eb7e03b130ca2efba77b4d2692bb_8160479304295384345.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Remuria",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", fell,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4780,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2023/12/20/a5b8d23dd3fbe0969cc3ebce78f9c29f_8021351765588020911.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Egeria",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "received a shard of the Primordial One and gained both godhood and the divine duty-come-lately, becoming the first Hydro Archon.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4809,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/02/237301566/8694aaf89d32e75eca416ec7fe41e487_7965225301501951666.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Натлан",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "There was no Archon War in Natlan. The first Pyro Archon was a mortal,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7074,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/10/237301566/e7f7eee058f60fc225b1f5bc654a08e0_6006799746535018143.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Xbalanque",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", who defeated the Pyro Sovereign,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7298,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Xiuhcoatl",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", and got the powers from one of the four",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7086,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/16/237301566/693da8a1b01352fde999598e49b34fde_6627231214957224464.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
